&lt;h3&gt;What's in the Nwazet Google CODER Jetpack?&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Nwazet Google CODER Jetpack is &lt;strong&gt;pre-assembled and ready to go out-of-the-box with zero configuration required&lt;/strong&gt;. Just plug it into your network, add power and get coding!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Jetpack includes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1x Raspberry Pi Model B&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1x Nwazet MiniTux Case, stylish Green or
Black design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1x SanDisk 8 GB Class 10  SD Card with Google CODER v4
pre-installed, for super-responsive web sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1x Ethernet cable, for
maximum speed and zero configuration out of the box!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1x 5.5V 1A USB power adapter, perfect
for powering the Raspberry Pi&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1x 3' foot MicroUSB cable, to connect the Pi to the USB power adapter&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

